query:
SELECT 
                    m.title,
                    m.rating,
                    c.name as director,
                    COUNT(mc.cast_id) as cast_count,
                    (SELECT AVG(rating) FROM movies) as avg_rating
                FROM movies m
                LEFT JOIN celebrities c ON m.director_id = c.celebrity_id
                LEFT JOIN movie_cast mc ON m.movie_id = mc.movie_id
                WHERE m.rating > 8.0
                GROUP BY m.movie_id, m.title, m.rating, c.name
                HAVING cast_count > 0
                ORDER BY m.rating DESC
                LIMIT 10
raw_query:
SELECT 
                    m.title,
                    m.rating,
                    c.name as director,
                    COUNT(mc.cast_id) as cast_count,
                    (SELECT AVG(rating) FROM movies) as avg_rating
                FROM movies m
                LEFT JOIN celebrities c ON m.director_id = c.celebrity_id
                LEFT JOIN movie_cast mc ON m.movie_id = mc.movie_id
                WHERE m.rating > 8.0
                GROUP BY m.movie_id, m.title, m.rating, c.name
                HAVING cast_count > 0
                ORDER BY m.rating DESC
                LIMIT 10

query:
SELECT 
                    m.title,
                    m.rating,
                    c.name as director,
                    COUNT(mc.cast_id) as cast_count,
                    (SELECT AVG(rating) FROM movies) as avg_rating
                FROM movies m
                LEFT JOIN celebrities c ON m.director_id = c.celebrity_id
                LEFT JOIN movie_cast mc ON m.movie_id = mc.movie_id
                WHERE m.rating > 8.0
                GROUP BY m.movie_id, m.title, m.rating, c.name
                HAVING cast_count > 0
                ORDER BY m.rating DESC
                LIMIT 10
raw_query:
SELECT 
                    m.title,
                    m.rating,
                    c.name as director,
                    COUNT(mc.cast_id) as cast_count,
                    (SELECT AVG(rating) FROM movies) as avg_rating
                FROM movies m
                LEFT JOIN celebrities c ON m.director_id = c.celebrity_id
                LEFT JOIN movie_cast mc ON m.movie_id = mc.movie_id
                WHERE m.rating > 8.0
                GROUP BY m.movie_id, m.title, m.rating, c.name
                HAVING cast_count > 0
                ORDER BY m.rating DESC
                LIMIT 10
